SkyCover Infrastructure installation CD-ROM

https://redmine.skycover.ru/projects/sci-cd/

This is the Debian/GNU Linux custom CD-ROM, which helps to

* Install Ganeti cluster with Xen and DRBD (http://code.google.com/p/ganeti/)
* Tune (automatically) over 25 Xen Linux system parameters
* Set up virtual instance with Puppet master, BIND9 and Approx
* Run Linux and Windows virtual machines

Includes:

* XEN-hypervisor 4.0 amd64
* Dom0 amd64
* drbd
* vlan
* ganeti
* puppet
* zabbix client
* amanda client
* and various tools

You'll need "uuencode" (sharutils) to build the project.

Read OVERVIEW next.
